## Priority: High

Only `@event` shorthand works. Full `v-on:event` syntax, dynamic arguments, and modifiers are rejected.

## Scope

- Accept `v-on:click` as equivalent to `@click`
- Event modifiers: `.stop`, `.prevent`, `.self`, `.once`, `.capture`, `.passive`
- Key modifiers: `@keyup.enter`, `@keyup.esc`
- Generate modifier wrapping in codegen (e.g., `event.stopPropagation()`)